# Security Hardening Status

## Deliverables

| File | Status | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| `apps/api/internal/security/hardening.go` | DONE | TLS 1.3 config, secure listener with timeouts, hardened http.Server |
| `apps/api/internal/security/headers.go` | DONE | Security headers middleware: HSTS, CSP, X-Frame-Options, etc. |
| `apps/api/internal/security/rate_limit.go` | DONE | Token-bucket rate limiter per IP with cleanup goroutine |
| `apps/api/internal/security/waf.go` | DONE | WAF rules for SQLi, XSS, path traversal, cmd injection |
| `security/pentest/owasp-top-10.md` | DONE | OWASP Top 10:2021 testing checklist with tools & references |
| `security/fuzz/ssh_fuzz.go` | DONE | SSH protocol fuzzer with random payloads |

## Notes
- `randInt` helper in fuzzer is a stub and should be replaced with `math/rand/v2` or `crypto/rand` in production.
- WAF rules are regex-based and may need tuning for false positives.
- Rate limiter defaults: 1 req/sec per IP, burst of 5.
- HSTS max-age: 1 year with includeSubDomains and preload.
- TLS 1.3 only, modern cipher suites enforced.
